# Zyrakon - Cloudflare Redirects
# URL forwarding rules

# Force www to apex
https://www.zyrakon.com/*    https://zyrakon.com/:splat    301

# Trailing slash normalization
/pages/about/    /pages/about    301
/pages/products/ /pages/products 301

# Legacy redirects (future-proofing)
/old-site/*      /               301
/blog            /pages/resources  301
/docs            /pages/developers 301
/api             /pages/developers 301
/security        /pages/trust-center 301
/privacy         /pages/legal     301
/terms           /pages/legal     301
/career          /pages/careers   301
